ENTRY       EC 1.14.13.143              Enzyme
NAME        ent-isokaurene C2-hydroxylase;
            CYP71Z6
CLASS       Oxidoreductases;
            Acting on paired donors, with incorporation or reduction of molecular oxygen;
            With NADH or NADPH as one donor, and incorporation of one atom of oxygen into the other donor
SYSNAME     ent-isokaurene,NADPH:oxygen oxidoreductase (hydroxylating)
REACTION    ent-isokaurene + O2 + NADPH + H+ = ent-2alpha-hydroxyisokaurene + H2O + NADP+ [RN:R09861]
