PRODUCT     ent-2alpha-hydroxyisokaurene [CPD:C20146];
            H2O [CPD:C00001];
            NADP+ [CPD:C00006]
COMMENT     This is the initial step in the conversion of ent-isokaurene to the antibacterial oryzalides in rice, Oryza sativa.
